void switchCase4(char grade, int x){    switch(grade){ 		case 'A' : 		case 'B' :{ 			/*Inner switch-case*/ 			switch (x){ 				case 1:  					x++; 					break; 				case -1:  					x--; 					break; 			} 			break; 		} 		default : 		  cout << "Invalid grade" << endl;    } }
